snippet.title: Hive Time Informational Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Hive Time is a cute and zany hive builder, updated for World Bee Day with a new Beepedia and many other improvements/fixes. Available now for Linux, MacOS (version 10.14 or lower) and Windows!

Want to know what Phil, Tracy, Jeff, and Amy are saying in this trailer? There's an English transcription here: http://hivetime.twolofbees.com/uploads/2020/informational_update_trailer_script.txt

Website: http://hivetime.twolofbees.com/

Itch.io: https://cheeseness.itch.io/hive-time

Twitter: https://twitter.com/hive_time/

Bandcamp: https://kestrelpi.bandcamp.com/album/hive-time
